							<p><strong>Coronavirus Update (April 2, 2020)</strong> <i class="alert-new-5823 fa fa-exclamation-triangle" style="display: none;"></i></p>
														<div class="school-list">
							<a title="Aurora Heights Elementary" href="our-schools/aurora-heights-elementary">Aurora Heights Elementary</a> | <a title="Berg Middle School" href="our-schools/berg-middle-school">Berg Middle School</a> | <a title="Emerson Hough Elementary" href="our-schools/emerson-hough-elementary">Emerson Hough Elementary</a> | <a title="Newton High School" href="our-schools/newton-high-school">Newton High School</a> | <a title="Thomas Jefferson Elementary" href="our-schools/thomas-jefferson-elementary">Thomas Jefferson Elementary</a> | <a title="WEST Academy" href="our-schools/west-academy">WEST Academy</a> | <a title="Woodrow Wilson Elementary" href="our-schools/woodrow-wilson-elementary">Woodrow Wilson Elementary</a> | <a title="E.J.H. Beard Administration Center" href="our-schools/ejhbeardadministrationcenter">E.J.H. Beard Administration Center</a>							</div>
														<p>Please see attached <a href="/Downloads/Coronavirus-Update-040220.pdf">communication</a> from Superintendent Bob Callaghan regarding an update on the Corona Virus, and school closure through April 30, 2020.</p>
						</div>
												
						<div class="carousel-item  alert-item alert-item-5808" data-alert="5808">
							<p class="legend alert-new-5808" style="display:none;"><i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Indicates a new alert</p>
							<p><strong>Social/Emotional Resources (March 26, 2020)</strong> <i class="alert-new-5808 fa fa-exclamation-triangle" style="display: none;"></i></p>
														<div class="school-list">
							<a title="Aurora Heights Elementary" href="our-schools/aurora-heights-elementary">Aurora Heights Elementary</a> | <a title="Berg Middle School" href="our-schools/berg-middle-school">Berg Middle School</a> | <a title="Emerson Hough Elementary" href="our-schools/emerson-hough-elementary">Emerson Hough Elementary</a> | <a title="Newton High School" href="our-schools/newton-high-school">Newton High School</a> | <a title="Thomas Jefferson Elementary" href="our-schools/thomas-jefferson-elementary">Thomas Jefferson Elementary</a> | <a title="WEST Academy" href="our-schools/west-academy">WEST Academy</a> | <a title="Woodrow Wilson Elementary" href="our-schools/woodrow-wilson-elementary">Woodrow Wilson Elementary</a> | <a title="E.J.H. Beard Administration Center" href="our-schools/ejhbeardadministrationcenter">E.J.H. Beard Administration Center</a>							</div>
														<p>The K-12 counselors have compiled a list of resources to support the social and emotional needs of our students and families. As with all the resources we have and will provide they are optional for you to use at your discretion. Please know that we are all thinking of you during this school closure and want everyone to be safe and healthy.</p>
<p><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YwkrE7vTwoi8rN8bgquDTr4dDWEd7PVpDUiPbsyu9Hs/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Social/Emotional Resources</a>
</p>
<p>Bret Miller </p>
<p>Director of Teaching and Learning</p>
						</div>
												
						<div class="carousel-item  alert-item alert-item-5721" data-alert="5721">
