							<p><strong>GRAB N GO FREE MEALS (18 &amp; Under):  (UPDATE: April 6, 2020)</strong> <i class="alert-new-5721 fa fa-exclamation-triangle" style="display: none;"></i></p>
														<div class="school-list">
							<a title="Aurora Heights Elementary" href="our-schools/aurora-heights-elementary">Aurora Heights Elementary</a> | <a title="Berg Middle School" href="our-schools/berg-middle-school">Berg Middle School</a> | <a title="Emerson Hough Elementary" href="our-schools/emerson-hough-elementary">Emerson Hough Elementary</a> | <a title="Newton High School" href="our-schools/newton-high-school">Newton High School</a> | <a title="Thomas Jefferson Elementary" href="our-schools/thomas-jefferson-elementary">Thomas Jefferson Elementary</a> | <a title="WEST Academy" href="our-schools/west-academy">WEST Academy</a> | <a title="Woodrow Wilson Elementary" href="our-schools/woodrow-wilson-elementary">Woodrow Wilson Elementary</a> | <a title="E.J.H. Beard Administration Center" href="our-schools/ejhbeardadministrationcenter">E.J.H. Beard Administration Center</a>							</div>
														<p>The Newton Community School District continues to offer an emergency food program during school closure.  We have been happy to serve you at our two sites!  </p>
<p><strong>Curbside breakfast &amp; lunch pick up:</strong></p>
<p><strong>*Starting April 6, 2020</strong> - pickup will only be on <strong>Monday</strong> (3 meals) &amp; <strong>Thursday</strong> (2 meals)</p>
<p>11: 00 AM - 12:30 PM</p>
<p>Berg Middle School</p>
<p>Newton High School</p>
<ul>
<li>Children do not need to be present at time of pick up</li>
<li>FREE McDonald's Happy Meal coupon will be included (while supplies last)</li>
</ul>
<p>Grab N Go Meals - Menu:  <a href="/Downloads/2020-meal-plan-April-13-16.pdf">Menu April 13 &amp; 16</a> / <a href="/Downloads/2020-meal-plan-April-20-23.pdf">April 20 &amp; 23</a><br></p>
